    <note>Yin(2) Gou [7405] Since he was 10 year old when his father died (see Han Qi's funerary inscription for Zhu), he must have been 39, not 31, years old when he died. Zhu's [7104] third son, Fan(2) Chunren [559] was his wife's in-law. Co-opted into initial office by Han(1) Qi [630]. Son-in-law of Li(2) Changling's [974] son or nephew, Yuqing(2) [3553]. Fan Chunren, WJ, 15.17b-19b; Yin Zhu, WJ, 28.35b. CBD, 1, 97-8.</note>
